snippet.title: Expeditions: A MudRunner Game – World Premiere Reveal | Opening Night Live 2023
snippet.description:
Wishlist Expeditions: A Mudrunner Game now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2477340/Expeditions_A_MudRunner_Game?utm_campaign=Expedition_ONLRevealTrailer&utm_medium=description&utm_source=YouTube

Embark on ever-rewarding scientific expeditions as you adapt to nature's challenges and unravel the mysteries of uncharted lands. Expeditions: A MudRunner Game is the new off-road adventure game developped by the experts of the genre, Saber Interactive.  

The game will be released on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch and PC.
